description.en: KONGZ20 is a tokenized derivative of the CyberKongz NFT collection. It enables anyone to trade NFTs from the collection in a permissionless way with instant liquidity on https://nft20.io/ routed via UniSwap. Every 100 KONGZ20 tokens represent an underlying CyberKongz NFT, minted upon deposit in the pool on https://nft20.io/ and burned upon withdrawal from the pool.
